fields.name: Chanel Transparent Vanity Flap Backpack
fields.description: Transparent might be the future-fashion-thing, but it doesn’t provide privacy. But what’s good about the Vanity Flap Backpack is the double option. The top features a leather flap with transparent body. The flap resembles the iconic Classic Flap Bag, which is both gorgeous and stylish. You can store your essentials inside this compartment, but everyone will see it. And so, if you have more important essentials that you don’t want anyone to see, you can simply use the vanity case below.

fields.name: Women's Limited Edition Green Quilted Lambskin Leather Cc Backpack
fields.description: The interior is lined with canvas. Moderate corner wear. Marking to exterior flap of bag. Faint scratching to hardware. Minor creasing throughout. Loss of shape.

fields.name: Chanel Drawstring Bucket Bag in Black
fields.description: Crafted from navy blue diamond-quilted leather, this drawstring bucket bag displays the iconic motif to the front for an instantly recognisable look.

fields.name: Chanel Small Gabrielle Bucket Bag
fields.description: This small Gabrielle bucket bag from the 2017 collection features a white leather soft body covered with two black quilted leather parts connected with small ruthenium chains. Featuring a ruthenium and gold coated chain entwined with white leather. Closing with an iconic CC gold coated clasp and with a red satin interior. Made in France.

fields.name: Chanel Women Mini Bucket Bag Calfskin Imitation Pearls Gold Tone Metal White
fields.description: Chanel bucket bag If you already own your preferred leather bag, go with this flap bag decorated with pearl and caviar. The mini measurement makes it ideal for going out at night. Chanel in each period contains some fantastic works, their latest is this bucket clutch. This can of course be paired with a ruffled tulle dress for a fantastic look, or with your favorite shirt and shorts.

fields.name: Chanel bucket bag
fields.description: Chanel bucket bag Caviar grain leather pearlescent series, adjustable shoulder strap length

fields.name: Chanel medium Double Flap shoulder bag
fields.description: Beige lambskin 1992 medium Double Flap shoulder bag from Chanel featuring diamond quilting, leather and chain-link shoulder strap, signature double flap closure, signature interlocking CC turn-lock fastening, main compartment, internal slip pocket, internal patch pockets, internal zip-fastening pocket, internal signature interlocking CC logo, internal logo stamp, slip pocket to the rear, gold-tone hardware and circa 1992.

fields.name: Chanel 1985-1993 mini diamond quilt chain crossbody bag
fields.description: Boasting the signature diamond quilting introduced by Gabrielle Chanel in 1955, this crossbody bag from Chanel is crafted from black leather. Decorated with an interlocking CC Turnlock to the front, gold-tone hardware finishes the piece.

fields.name: Pink Quilted Matte Caviar Leather Classic Medium Double Flap Bag
fields.description: Don't miss out on your opportunity to get this stunning Chanel Pink Quilted Matte Caviar Leather Classic Medium Double Flap Bag. It features sleek matte textured caviar leather and a silvertone CC turn-lock closure. Wear it with jeans or an evening dress, and look fabulous without even trying!

fields.name: Chanel Classic Red Quilted Lambskin Leather CC Rhinestones Flap Shoulder Bag
fields.description: Vintage 80s Chanel classic red quilted lambskin leather flap shoulder bag. Featuring gold toned CC rhinestones flap, snap button closure, gold chain with red leather shoulder strap, interior open pocket. A classic with a twisted Chanel red leather shoulder bag is rare.

fields.name: Metallic Classic Chanel
fields.description: Introduced by Gabrielle Chanel to guarantee the quality and durability of leather bags, diamond quilting has become one of Chanel's signatures. That, combined with the leather and chain-link shoulder strap and the iconic interlocking CC turn-lock,

fields.name: Chanel Black Leather Gold Carryall Travel Stitch Top Handle Satchel Bag
fields.description: A modern reinterpretation of the classic diamond quilting, Chanel's Wild Stitch quilting easily became one of the maison's signatures. Crafted from lambskin in a black hue, this top-handle bag is finished with contrasting beige stitching.

fields.name: Chanel Mini Timeless shoulder bag
fields.description: Introduced by Gabrielle Chanel to guarantee the quality and durability of leather bags, diamond quilting has become one of Chanel's signatures. That, combined with the leather and chain-link shoulder strap and the iconic interlocking CC logo, results in this 1996–1997 Timeless diamond-quilted flap shoulder bag

fields.name: CHANEL Quilted Leather CC Logo Shoulder Bag Red
fields.description: Guaranteed Authentic Chanel Shoulder Bag or 100% of your money back. This vintage bag is in red quilted leather with gold tone hardware. It features frontal CC logo, leather woven chain handles, click lock closure, and a spacious red interior with one zipped pocket.

fields.name: CHANEL Matelasse Tassel fringe Shoulder Bag Lambskin Leather Green
fields.description: CHANEL Matelasse Tassel fringe Shoulder Bag Lambskin Leather Green

fields.name: CHANEL VINTAGE CAVIAR GRAND SHOPPING TOTE BAG WITH GOLD HARDWARE NM
fields.description: Two compartments, two zip pockets, one slip pocket

fields.name: Chanel LARGE TOTE
fields.description: Mixed Fibers & Silver-Tone Metal Black

fields.name: Chanel Deauville Pearl Tote Bag
fields.description: The Chanel Deauville tote bag first appeared on the runway of Chanel’s SS12 collection and was clearly an instant classic in the fashion world. The simple yet beautiful design of this bag struck a chord with many and the Deauville proceeded to become a fast favourite. Chanel has continued to bring out this shape in a multitude of their collections, updating colours, hardware and materials to suit the season and collection themes. Named after one of Coco Chanel’s favourite beach resorts in Normandy, the Deauville screams summer and has us picturing ourselves on the beach with our Chanel tote by our side.

fields.name: Ophidia Gucci small backpack
fields.description: A versatile style that can be used as a travel accessory or a bookbag, the backpack continues to be an important silhouette in the world of Gucci, offered in a variety of sizes and interpretations. Part of the ever-expanding world of Ophidia, it's crafted in GG Supreme canvas with textured leather trim. The inlaid green and red Web detail and Double G hardware are steeped in the House's rich history, referencing symbols incorporated in Gucci collections since the '50s.

fields.name: Gucci Black backpack
fields.description: The GG motif in a distinct black/grey combination is further enriched with Web straps and black leather trims. Made in soft GG Supreme, a softer version of GG Supreme canvas, crafted from a coated microfibre fabric with the GG motif.

fields.name: Gucci Eden small backpack
fields.description: Small GG Supreme canvas backpack, finished with black leather details. A versatile design that can be used as a bookbag or travel accessory, the backpack is crafted from monogram fabric pulled straight from the '70s archives.

fields.name: Ophidia Gucci medium backpack
fields.description: With a hiking pack inspired shape, the medium-sized backpack is crafted in GG Supreme canvas contrasted with technical mesh details. A classic combination of the House's most recognisable elements—the GG motif and Web stripe—the world of Ophidia continues to evolve, incorporating new shapes and silhouettes. The bag is finished with the Double G hardware which defines the line.

fields.name: Gucci Marmont mini bucket bag
fields.description: The world of GG Marmont expands with the introduction of a mini bucket bag shape in black matelassé leather with a chevron motif. Inspired by an archival design from the '70s—a hallmark era of the House—the Double G decorates the front of this accessory. Featuring a chain strap and drawstring closure the versatile shape can also be worn as a cross body bag.

fields.name: Ophidia GG mini bucket bag
fields.description: Gucci's Ophidia GG bucket bag is small in stature but big on style. The compact design is rendered in the Italian brand's hallmark beige-toned, monogram-adorned canvas, with signature red and green Sylvie Web stripes running around the base. Brown-toned leather trims complete the design with an elegant touch, along with a butter-soft suede lining.

fields.name: Gucci Marmont mini bucket bag
fields.description: A mini bucket bag presented in white matelassé leather with a heart detail on the back. The GG Marmont collection is defined by the emblematic Double G hardware—a contemporary take on a Gucci archival belt buckle from the '70s that has become a hallmark of the House. Completed by a gold-toned chain strap, the dynamic shape can be worn in multiple ways.

fields.name: Gucci Horsebit 1955 small shoulder bag
fields.description: The Horsebit has become synonymous with the brand. Tracing back to Gucci's equestrian roots, the double ring and bar design is a piece of the House's heritage. Inspired by archival designs, the Gucci Horsebit 1955 unifies original details first introduced over six decades ago with a modern spirit. For Epilogue, the line is enriched with a small shoulder bag in GG Supreme canvas with contrasting white leather details and a special mechanism that adjusts the length of the shoulder strap so it can be carried on one shoulder or cross body.

fields.name: Ophidia mini Gucci Supreme cross-body bag
fields.description: Alessandro Michele turns to a number of Gucci’s house signatures for this brown Ophidia cross-body mini bag. It’s crafted in Italy from iconic GG Supreme canvas set with the storied red and green Web stripes – originally inspired by vintage saddled straps – while the logo plaque has been used since the 1970s. Adjust the long shoulder strap to wear it across everyday looks.

fields.name: Small Gucci Supreme Ophidia Shoulder Bag
fields.description: A classic combination of Gucci’s most recognisable elements is one of the first things you see in the Ophidia shoulder bag. The retro design is characterised by its domed shape and GG Supreme canvas inlaid with the two-tone Web stripe detail – continuing to pay homage to the House’s Italian roots. The leather trims are combined with gold-tone hardware and the classic Double G logo, which is also added as charms on the zip pull to unveil a silk lining inside.

fields.name: Gucci Marmont matelassé mini bag
fields.description: The mini GG Marmont chain shoulder bag has a softly structured shape and a zip top closure with Double G hardware. The chain shoulder strap has a leather shoulder detail. The camera bag is made in matelassé leather with a chevron design and GG on the back.

fields.name: Gucci Marmont matelassé shoulder bag
fields.description: The small GG Marmont chain shoulder bag has a softly structured shape and an oversized flap closure with Double G hardware. The sliding chain strap can be worn multiple ways, changing between a shoulder and a top handle bag. Made in matelassé chevron leather with a heart on the back.

fields.name: Gucci Marmont super mini bag
fields.description: A part of the Beloved universe, the GG Marmont is instantly recognizable by its matelassé leather and monogram hardware. Together, the Beloved lines come together to represent the Creative Director's vision over the last seven years. This super mini bag adds a contemporary element to the bag with a deep blue shade.

fields.name: GUCCI Brown Calfskin Leather Vintage Web Medium Webby Satchel Bag
fields.description: Clean lines and a functional silhouette are some of the things we love about this satchel from Gucci! Made from beautiful calfskin leather, this tote is paired with the classic red and green vintage webbing, and two toting handles. The interior has just enough room to hold all of your daily essentials! You'll love this casual, yet classy everyday bag!

fields.name: Gucci Brown Leather GG Monogram Coated Canvas Satchel Grab Bag HandBag
fields.description: This chic satchel is crafted of Gucci GG monogram coated canvas in beige with brown leather trimming. The bag features two double rolled leather handles, a removable strap and gold tone hardware. The zipper top opens to a fully leather lined interior with a zipper pocket and tag with authenticity code. This amazing bag is ideal for everyday use to keep all your girly essentials in check, from Gucci!

fields.name: Ophidia Gucci medium tote
fields.description: A classic combination of the House's most defining codes—the GG motif and Web stripe—the world of Ophidia continues to evolve, incorporating new shapes and silhouettes each season. With recognizable design elements in a practical new shape, this new medium sized tote is trimmed with textured leather and topped with Double G hardware. Thanks to its long leather handles, the style can also be carried as a shoulder bag.

fields.name: Gucci Off The Grid tote bag
fields.description: A line of accessories and ready-to-wear is presented for Pre-Fall 2020 made from recycled materials and trims, supporting the House's commitment to sustainability. Gucci Off The Grid is the first collection from Gucci Circular Lines—a concept created to support the House's vision for circular production. Designed for those mindful of their environmental impact, Gucci Off The Grid uses recycled, organic, bio-based and sustainably sourced materials. Regenerated nylon, crafted using recycled sewing thread and trims displays the GG pattern against an opaque background in black. Crafted into a double handled tote bag, the shape is finished with an optional shoulder strap that can be detached on one side and stored within the bag.

fields.name: The Marc Jacobs Backpack
fields.description: The Marc Jacobs logo lettering forms an all-over print across this Marc Jacobs Kids backpack, commanding a classic schoolyard design with the label’s sense of logocentric flair. From the walk to school to exciting weekend adventures, this companion piece is an exemplary addition to your youngster’s growing accessory collection, ticking all of the boxes when it comes to both storage and style.

fields.name: Marc Jacobs 'The Backpack' logo-print backpack
fields.description: Marc Jacobs' The Backpack is realised in all-over leopard print. Crafted from cotton, the backpack is built with adjustable straps and a double zip-around closure. Its interior houses a spacious main compartment and back wall pocket. A zipped pouch compartment and side pockets also feature to the exterior.

fields.name: Marc Jacobs Women's Black Appliquéd Printed Shell Backpack
fields.description: Backpack Printed Shell Silver hardware Eyelets Patch Leather trims Two adjustable shoulder straps Detachable key fob Detachable charm Two-way zip fastening along top and sides Zipped front pocket This bag will fit your essentials, plus a tablet.

fields.name: MARC JACOBS The Pouch Nylon Backpack In Blue
fields.description: Blue/black The Zipper backpack from Marc Jacobs featuring logo patch to the front, single top handle, adjustable shoulder straps, all-around zip fastening, main compartment, internal slip pocket, internal logo patch, front zip-fastening pocket, front zip-fastening compartment and silver-tone hardware.

fields.name: The Marc Jacobs The Bucket Bag Leather Crossbody Bag
fields.description: The bucket bag leather crossbody bag in cream

fields.name: Marc Jacobs The Bucket Bag
fields.description: Grained coated leather bucket bag highlighted with goldtone logo hardware, finished with adjustable striped strap.

fields.name: MARC JACOBS Mini Rider Crossbody Bag
fields.description: Versatile saddle shaped bag with classic goldtone hardware..

fields.name: The Marc Jacobs Everyday Cross-Body Bag
fields.description: True to its name, The Marc Jacobs Everyday cross-body bag will be a faithful companion through all your day and nighttime adventures. A compartmentalised zip function and just-compact-enough size offer practicality, while the gold-tone chain strap adds instant polish – whether you wear it across the body or double it up to sling over the shoulder.

fields.name: MARC JACOBS CROSSBODY BAG WOMEN LEATHER VIOLET
fields.description: women's crossbody bag in violet designed by Marc Jacobs. It has features like front detail, side detail.

fields.name: Marc Jacobs Square Shaped Crossbody Bag - Yellow
fields.description: Marc Jacobs embraces a youthful energy around the collection - with emphasis upon detailing and a bohemian theme. From form-fitting minimalist silhouettes to sleek tailored pieces, the brand has stylish unique pieces for every occasion. This yellow leather square shaped crossbody bag from Marc Jacobs featuring a round top handle, a shoulder strap and silver-tone hardware.

fields.name: Quilted Medium Tote Bag Marc Jacobs
fields.description: A medium sized tote bag is perfect for a go-anywhere style and features a quilted design.

fields.name: Marc Jacobs Quilted Cross Body Bag
fields.description: Navy quilted leather crossbody bag with gold-tone hardware and chain strap. Foldover front with clasp fastening.

fields.name: NWT Marc by Marc Jacobs Too Hot to Handle Leather Satchel Crossbody Bag BLACK
fields.description: NWT Marc by Marc Jacobs Too Hot to Handle Leather Satchel Crossbody Bag BLACK

fields.name: Marc Jacobs Voyager Mini Satchel Crossbody
fields.description: Timeless mini faux leather satchel crossbody bag finished with goldtone logo hardware with lobster clasp on the strap..

fields.name: MARC JACOBS (THE)SNAPSHOT LEATHER SHOULDER BAG
fields.description: Detachable, adjustable logo web shoulder strap

fields.name: MARC JACOBS THE SOFTSHOT 21 IN CEMENT & BLACK
fields.description: Two compartments, three card slots

fields.name: MARC JACOBS The Large Jacquard Tote
fields.description: This large tote from Marc Jacobs is a go-to for busy days. Boldly printed with the label's name, it's woven from durable cotton canvas and opens up to reveal a spacious interior that's fitted with a zipped pocket to keep you organised.

fields.name: THE TOTE BAG MARC JACOBS
fields.description: Large canvas tote featuring screen printed logo and top zipper closure. This item is part of THE COLOR COLLECTION, an everyday capsule designed by Marc to celebrate comfort, creativity and self-expression.

fields.name: MARC JACOBS The The small canvas tote bag - Black
fields.description: Made of cotton, the Small Tote is the leading bag from the Marc Jacobs label. This minimalist model, offered in dark and vibrant shades, is back again for the Autumn-Winter 2021 season. The ultimate practical and elegant essential to suit everyone's style.

fields.name: Mulberry Heritage Backpack Mole & Cognac Scotchgrain
fields.description: The Heritage collection was designed in tribute to the early bags of Mulberry, which were inspired by English country pursuits. The Heritage Backpack features practical pockets, belt and buckle strap detailing and a signature logo plaque. The straps can be adjusted to a personal fit and all your belongings are secured under the front flap.

fields.name: Mulberry Zipped Backpack Pale Navy Heavy Grain
fields.description: The Zipped Backpack offers function and form in an equal partnership. The sleek silhouette has two zipped compartments that offer a convenient way to carry around your necessities.

fields.name: Mulberry Abbey Small Classic Grain Leather Bucket Bag, Oxblood
fields.description: The Abbey is a traditional bucket bag with drawstring detailing, contrast lining and a range of eye-catching or iconic leather finishes. The Abbey features the recognisable postman's pock as a nod to Mulberry's heritage DNA, securing a simple belt closure on a timeless, easy to wear style. Complete with a small internal zip pouch to keep valuable possessions safe.

fields.name: Mulberry Lynton Mini Bucket Bag
fields.description: Mulberry mini Lynton bucket bag in grey-green smooth nlamb nappa leather with the label's moniker in gold-tone lettering at front. Comes with a gold-tone metal chain and is lined in deep burgundy leather with one credit card slot. Has been carried once and is in virtually new condition. Comes with dust bag.

fields.name: MULBERRY Darley branded leather cross-body bag
fields.description: Detachable and adjustable leather shoulder strap, branded gold-toned hardware, one main compartment, three credit card slots, nappa lined, all-over grainy bovine leather texture.

fields.name: Mulberry Amberley satchel small
fields.description: Oak brown leather Amberley satchel small from Mulberry featuring an adjustable shoulder strap, foldover top with twist-lock closure and an internal slip pocket.

fields.name: Mulberry Small Darley Small Classic Grain Leather Cross Body Bag, Pale Slate
fields.description: The Small Darley is iconic with the Mulberry signature Postman's Lock and is perfect for carrying essentials or used to keep valuables secure inside an everyday bag. The Nappa lined interior features eight credit card slots, a zip pocket and two slip pockets. Additionally, there's a useful gusseted zip pocket on the back of the bag. This version is crafted from classic grained leather and can be transformed into a mini bag thanks to its detachable chain strap

fields.name: MULBERRY Darley quilted leather shoulder bag
fields.description: Dual-length chain strap, back slip pocket, two main compartments, internal slip pocket, quilted finish, silver-toned hardware, engraved logo

fields.name: Mulberry Small Darley Quilted Metallic Buffalo Leather Shoulder Bag, Antique Gold
fields.description: A celebration of Mulberry's signature Postman's Lock and the iconic Darley Bag, the new Darley Shoulder Bag offers a refined and contemporary silhouette for everyday that is elegant enough for the evening. This small version in quilted leather offers a flap-over style with a roomy interior containing slip pockets that help organise your essentials. The chain and leather strap complete the look and make this style easy to carry.

fields.name: MULBERRY Alexa Oversized Satchel Bag
fields.description: Revived from the archives for its 10th anniversary, Mulberry’s Alexa is a laid-back take on the traditional satchel. The oversized iteration is crafted from soft grained leather to create a relaxed shape and retains two iconic features from the original: a braided handle and a golden turn-lock closure. Style yours with an oversized blazer like the off-duty model that inspired it.

fields.name: MULBERRY Alexa Satchel Bag
fields.description: Revived from the archives for its 10th anniversary, Mulberry’s Alexa is a laid-back take on the traditional satchel. It’s crafted from soft grained leather to create a relaxed shape and retains two iconic features from the original: a braided handle and a golden turn-lock closure. Style yours with an oversized blazer like the off-duty models that inspired it.

fields.name: MULBERRY Darley Shoulder Bag
fields.description: Shorten or lengthen the gold-tone chain on the Darley shoulder Bag from Mulberry depending on your look, enjoying the heavy grain leather and postman lock details set across this classic style.

fields.name: Mulberry Antony Messenger Oak Natural Grain Leather
fields.description: The Antony Messenger is a functional and stylish unisex bag, designed in a slightly larger size than the classic Antony. Thoughtfully equipped, it features an adjustable canvas strap that can be worn across the body or over the shoulder. Instantly recognisable, it's finished with the iconic Postman's Lock.

fields.name: Mulberry Lily small shoulder bag
fields.description: Lily small shoulder bag

fields.name: Darley Shoulder Bag Mulberry Green Heavy Grain
fields.description: A celebration of our signature Postman's Lock and the iconic Darley Bag, the new Darley Shoulder Bag offers a refined and contemporary silhouette for everyday that is elegant enough for evening.

fields.name: Bayswater Tote Burgundy Small Classic Grain Mulberry
fields.description: The perfect everyday bag, the Bayswater Tote is eternally practical; spacious enough to fit essentials from an iPad to a pair of shoes. This classic style closes with the iconic Postman's Lock, and features a luxurious suede lining. Use the internal and removable pocket to store your most valued essentials.

fields.name: MULBERRY Bayswater Tote Bag
fields.description: It wouldn't be a Mulberry Bayswater without the line's signature Postman's lock closure. Crafted in a classic tote shape from the brand's deeply grained leather, the spacious interior is lined with suede and fits all the essentials from an iPad to a pair of shoes, while a removable pouch is perfect for storing your more fiddly bits..

fields.name: PRADA Nylon backpack
fields.description: Opt for an iconic Prada look with the label’s nylon backpack, which is just as coveted now as it was in the early ‘90s. Crafted in Italy, this design balances pragmatism with style; multiple pockets, buckle fastenings, and adjustable shoulder straps make it fully functional. It's finished with steel hardware – including the triangle logo plate – and saffiano leather trim, another signature of the label.

fields.name: Vintage Prada Backpack Black Green Silver hardware
fields.description: Vintage Prada backpack in green nylon with black leather details and silver hardware.

fields.name: Prada Brown Nylon Drawstring Backpack
fields.description: This Prada backpack is just what you need to complete your overall look. Incorporate the right flavour to your distinctive style option with this stunning brown bag. This nylon bag exudes an aura of excellence and an unequaled standard of craftsmanship.

fields.name: Prada Leather Bucket Bag
fields.description: The bag decorated with the triangle logo has a double shoulder strap, one in leather and the other in multicolored fabric

fields.name: Prada drawstring-fastening logo bucket bag
fields.description: Luxury Italian heritage and expert artisanal craftsmanship lie at the heart of Milanese fashion house Prada's coveted design aesthetic. Founded in 1913, the brand is known for producing timeless items with traditional craftsmanship. Add a dash of colour to your looks this season with this sunny yellow calf leather drawstring-fastening logo bucket bag from Prada. Featuring a gold-tone lettering logo to the front, a top handle, a detachable and adjustable shoulder strap, a drawstring fastening, a main internal compartment and an internal patch pocket.

fields.name: Prada Pink Diagramme Leather Camera Crossbody Bag
fields.description: Bags are more than just instruments to carry one's essentials. They tell a woman's sense of style and the better the bag, the more confidence she gets when she holds it. Prada brings you one such fabulous bag meticulously made from pink Diagramme leather carrying a quilted pattern all over. This shoulder bag is detailed with the brand logo in gold-tone. It has a nylon-lined interior featuring a slip pocket. The bag is complete with a chain-link shoulder strap.

fields.name: Prada sequinned logo-print mesh tote bag
fields.description: The accessories at Prada's AW21 runway show paid particular attention to the label's signature triangular logo plaque, which decorates the interior zipped pouch of this black tote bag. Designed with a mesh construction, it features sequin embellishments and a printed logo to the front.

fields.name: Prada Crossbody Bag
fields.description: This bandoleer bag in iconic Prada nylon has a woven nylon shoulder strap. The accessory with metal logo has an external zipper pocket and three inside pockets.

fields.name: Prada Leather tote
fields.description: This soft leather tote making its debut in the Fall Winter 2020 collection presents a new interpretation of the triangle logo that is traced by stitching and features the shiny Prada metal lettering logo at its center. Reverse stitching emphasizes the soft, rounded look of the silhouette, completed by long leather handles and a drawstring closure.
